1.切换到root账户：
sudo su

2 安装 MySQL 5
apt-get install mysql-server mysql-client
系统会提示你设置密码

3 安装 Nginx
apt-get install nginx
启动Nginx服务：
service nginx start
去浏览器看一下：http://localhost

5 设置 nginx ,修改文件：
vi /etc/nginx/nginx.conf
修改一些主机的基本配置

虚拟主机配置文件修改：
vi /etc/nginx/sites-enabled/default
增加如下代码，处理pathinfo的(要修改$rootdir的值)：
server {
    server_name localhost *.robin.com;
    listen 80;
    
    autoindex on;

    set $charset utf-8;

    charset $charset;

    set $rootdir /home/leo/workspace/localhost;
    set $project www;

    if ( $host ~* "^([^\.]+)\.robin\.com$" ) {
        set $project $1;
    }

    set $rootdir $rootdir/$project;
    root $rootdir;
    index index.php index.html;

    set $rewrite yes;

    location ~ ^/favicon\.ico$ {
        root $rootdir;
    }
    
    location ~* (.*).tpl {
        return 404;
    }

    if ( $request_uri ~* ^/(data|public|assets|crossdomain\.xml|index\.php|favicon\.ico) ) {
        set $rewrite no;
    }


    if ($rewrite ~* yes) {
        rewrite ^/(.*) /index.php/$1 last;
    }

    location ~ /(data|public|assets|crossdomain\.xml)
    {
        try_files $uri $uri/ /index.html;
    }

    location /doc/ {
    	alias /usr/share/doc/;
	autoindex on;
	allow 127.0.0.1;
	allow ::1;
	deny all;
    }

    location / {
	fastcgi_split_path_info ^(.+\.php)(/.+)$;
	# NOTE: You should have "cgi.fix_pathinfo = 0;" in php.ini
	
	# With php5-cgi alone:
	#fastcgi_pass 127.0.0.1:9000;
	# With php5-fpm:
	fastcgi_pass unix:/var/run/php5-fpm.sock;
	fastcgi_index index.php;
	include fastcgi_params;
    }
}
以下是普通的配置：

server {
    server_name *.robin.com;
    listen 80;

    autoindex on;

    set $charset utf-8;

    charset $charset;

    set $rootdir /home/workspace/robin.com;
    set $project www;

    if ( $host ~* "^([^\.]+)\.robin\.com" ) {
        set $project $1;
    }

    set $rootdir $rootdir/$project;
    root $rootdir;
    index index.php index.html;
    location / {
                # First attempt to serve request as file, then
                # as directory, then fall back to displaying a 404.
                try_files $uri $uri/ =404;
                # Uncomment to enable naxsi on this location
                # include /etc/nginx/naxsi.rules
    }

    location ~ \.php$ {
        fastcgi_split_path_info ^(.+\.php)(/.+)$;
        # NOTE: You should have "cgi.fix_pathinfo = 0;" in php.ini

        # With php5-cgi alone:
        #fastcgi_pass 127.0.0.1:9000;
        # With php5-fpm:
        fastcgi_pass unix:/var/run/php5-fpm.sock;
        fastcgi_index index.php;
        include fastcgi_params;
    }
}


注：如果无法获取path_info，则要在fastcgi_params文件中增加：
 # PHP only, required if PHP was built with --enable-force-cgi-redirect
 fastcgi_param   REDIRECT_STATUS     200;
 fastcgi_param PATH_INFO $fastcgi_path_info;
 fastcgi_param PATH_TRANSLATED $document_root$fastcgi_path_info;
 
重新加载nginx:
service nginx restart

记得修改/etc/hosts

4 安装 PHP5
apt-get install php5-fpm

如果此时报错，remove一下：

apt-get remove php5-snmp

安装好后执行 php -i

注意：此处如果报错，直接安装缺少组件即可

扩展：

查询PHP模块：
apt-cache search php5

例如输入下面安装你要的模块：
apt-get install php5-mysql php5-curl php5-gd php5-intl php-pear php5-imagick php5-imap php5-mcrypt php5-memcache php5-ming php5-ps php5-pspell php5-recode php5-snmp php5-sqlite php5-tidy php5-xmlrpc php5-xsl php5-redis
安装完毕之后重启php5-fpm
service php5-fpm restart


压力测试工具：
apt-get install siege

http://blog.csdn.net/wzy_1988/article/details/8112478

nginx.conf

add_header Access-Control-Allow-Origin *;                                                                                                               
add_header Access-Control-Allow-Headers X-Requested-With;                                                                                               
add_header Access-Control-Allow-Methods GET,POST,OPTIONS; 
    
